[SetUp "1"]
[UTCDate "2020.08.03"]
[UTCTime "02:16:38"]

25... h4 26. Bh2 g3! { With the initiative, White has to play fxg3 to save the bishop... } 27. fxg3 Be3+ { However, this leads to a forced checkmating pattern. } 28. Kf1 (28. Kh1 hxg3) 28... Qf6+ 29. Ke2 Qf2# { 0-1 Black wins by checkmate. } *


